  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1832175765" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1832175765" />
    <a title="Nancy Kotkin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10163038-nancy-kotkin"><img alt="Nancy Kotkin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1389914411p2/10163038.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1832175765?book_show_action=true">Dec 14, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nancy Kotkin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nancy Kotkin" href="/user/show/10163038-nancy-kotkin">Nancy Kotkin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=stars-4">stars-4</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=2016-pb-400">2016-pb-400</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=2016-reads">2016-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=grandparents">grandparents</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=folklore">folklore</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=picture-books">picture-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=pub-penguin-putnam">pub-penguin-putnam</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10163038-nancy-kotkin?shelf=pb-seasons">pb-seasons</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1832175765" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5072620859490373069">When a Ukrainian boy drops his brand new white mitten in the snow, a bunch of wild animals moves into it. Adapted from a Ukrainian folk tale. For this picture book, the typical Jan Brett sidebars are used to relate the boy&apos;s story while retaining the page&apos;s focus on the animals. Until, near the end, something happens to reverse the lenses. Solid story with beautiful illustrations, though not quite as good as <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/196951.The_Hat' title='The Hat by Jan Brett' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Hat</a>.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText5072620859490373069" style="display:none">When a Ukrainian boy drops his brand new white mitten in the snow, a bunch of wild animals moves into it. Adapted from a Ukrainian folk tale. For this picture book, the typical Jan Brett sidebars are used to relate the boy's story while retaining the page's focus on the animals. Until, near the end, something happens to reverse the lenses. Solid story with beautiful illustrations, though not quite as good as <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/196951.The_Hat" title="The Hat by Jan Brett" rel="nofollow noopener">The Hat</a>.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="5072620859490373069" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


